public sealed interface WritableElement<T> extends ClassfileElement permits Annotation, AnnotationElement, AnnotationValue, Attribute<A>, PoolEntry, BootstrapMethodEntry, FieldModel, MethodModel, ConstantPoolBuilder, DirectFieldBuilder, DirectMethodBuilder
A classfile element that can encode itself as a stream of bytes in the encoding expected by the classfile format.
